criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-75 years old; both sex;

          -  ECoG 0 or 1;

          -  Patients that would undergo biopsy or surgical operation with high ACE2 expression
             tumors such as colorectal cancer, renal cancer, pancreatic cancer, gastric cancer,
             liver cancer, lung cancer, brain cancer or suspected tumor.

          -  use 18F-FDG PET/CT as baseline evaluation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Significant hepatic or renal dysfunction;

          -  Is Pregnant or ready to pregnant;

          -  Cannot lie on their back for half an hour;

          -  Suffering from claustrophobia or other mental diseases;

          -  Refusal to join the clinical study;
